What's happening to EZTV?... I mean, True Blood's season 4 has been oversized from the start: 550mb?! That's too big already for me! I mean, the previous seasons' episodes used to be about 400mb and the quality was always TOP!

700mb?!!... Way too much for me! I lilke to burn each season in 2 DVDs - and this oversized files crap is going to make me used 3 instead - and probably just for 1 or 2 eps! :( It wouldn't be much of a problem, though, if the inherent quality improvement should compensate - but it doesn't... ;/

I love you, EZ guys, but... I don't know.............. ;(
